## File Organization

### Component Structure

```
src/components/component-name/
├── index.tsx
├── helpers.ts
├── constants.ts
├── types.ts
└── tests/
    ├── index.spec.tsx
    ├── [helper_name_1].spec.ts
    └── [helper_name_2].spec.ts
```

### Naming Conventions

- **Component directories**: Use snake_case (e.g., `auth_dialog/`, `user_profile/`)
- **Test files**: Use snake_case for helper test files (e.g., `handle_sign_in.spec.ts`, `validate_form.spec.ts`)
- **Each helper function should have its own separate test file**
- **Test directory**: Always use `tests/` (plural)
